Symbol : CONFIG_HZ_PERIODIC, CONFIG_NO_HZ_IDLE, CONFIG_NO_HZ_FULL 

Choice : Idle dynticks system (CONFIG_NO_HZ_IDLE)

Info   : It is recommended to choose Idle dynticks system if you use a laptop and power saving is a concern.
If performance is your only goal, Periodic timer ticks should be selected.

